## Overview

This Node.js + Express + Mongoose application fetches data from the public JSONPlaceholder API, caches it in MongoDB, and exposes endpoints to list, filter, and view post details.

## Endpoints

- **GET /api/fetch-data** → Fetches posts and users from JSONPlaceholder and caches them in MongoDB
- **GET /api/posts** → List all posts; supports optional query parameter `?userId=`
- **GET /api/posts/:id** → View post details including user info

